title: Trump says Ukraine are ungrateful for US peace deal efforts
description: US President Donald Trump has lashed out at Ukrainian leadership, claiming they are ungrateful for the US' efforts to secure a peace deal with Russia to end the war. #trump #potus #ukraine #peace #peacedeal

title: British PM says Andrew should give evidence in Epstein case
description: When asked whether disgraced former royal Andrew Mountbatten Windsor should testify in the Epstein case, British Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said "a general principle I have held onto is anybody who has information in relation to these matters should give that evidence". #sirkeirstarmer #andrewmountbattenwindsor #epstein #trump #uscongress

title: Staggering cost of new BoM website revealed
description: It has been revealed that the new Bureau of Meteorology website cost taxpayers nearly $100 million dollars. #bom #bureauofmeteorology #weather #website #taxpayer

title: At least 90 people killed in Vietnam floods
description: A week of heavy rain has caused severe flooding and landslides across Vietnam, killing at least 90 people and destroying almost 186,000 homes. #vietnam #flood #landslide #naturaldisaster #weather

title: CommBank is the first major bank to offer a construction loan for prefabricated houses
description: CommBank is the first major bank to offer a construction loan for prefabricated houses, with the product set to launch before Christmas. Prefabricated (prefab) homes are partially built in factories then moved to your land and built in.   For more on the prefab revolution listen to the latest episode of The Issue, or watch on YouTube. #TheIssue #CommBank #Housing

title: Gunmen on the run after violent home invasion
description: Police are hunting for three gunmen after a 26-year-old man was shot in the leg during a Penrith home invasion. #police #crime #investigation #westernsydney #penrith

title: Jonathan Bailey surprises Wicked: For Good fans at screening in Sydney
description: Prince Fiyero himself has made a surprise appearance at a Wicked: For Good screening in Sydney. Actor Jonathan Bailey is on holiday in Australia with his family, as the film rakes in huge money at the box office. #wicked #wickedforgood #jonathanbailey #imax #sydney

title: Snapchat reveals age verification plan ahead of social media ban for kids aged under 16
description: Snapchat will verify the age of users with photo ID, bank details, and facial age estimation technology when Australia's social media ban for kids aged under 16 begins in December. #snapchat #socialmedia #socialmediaban #facialrecognition #ageverification

title: Teen survives crocodile attack while fishing in Far North Queensland | 7NEWS
description: 17-year-old Dexter was bitten by a crocodile while fishing with friends in a creek south of Cairns. The teenager was walking through water in an area where they had never previously seen crocodiles when the reptile sat on his foot before attacking and biting him below his belly button. title: Widespread flooding in Darwin after Tropical Cyclone Fina batters Northern Territory capital
description: Widespread flooding is drenching Darwin after Tropical Cyclone Fina battered the city over the weekend. Residents are being urged to not drive through floodwaters and to stay away from fallen powerlines, as a massive clean-up begins in the Northern Territory capital. #darwin #tcfina #cyclone #tropicalcyclone #northernterritory

title: Storm supercell smashed South East Queensland
description: South East Queensland has been smashed by a supercell storm, delivering giant hail, heavy rain and destructive winds across the region. #Weather #WildWeather #Hail #Storm #Queensland

title: Golden Top Bakery goes up in flames at Marrickville in Sydney's inner west
description: Golden Top Bakery in Marrickville has gone up in flames on Monday morning. Around 80 firefighters were called to Barclay Street in Sydney's inner west just before 6.30am after the blaze broke out inside the building. #marrickville #sydney #fire #fireandrescue #frnsw
